Content:: Castelnau-Magnoac (French pronunciation: [kastɛlno maɲɔak]; Occitan: Castèthnau de Manhoac) is a commune in the Hautes-Pyrénées department in south-western France.  This Hautes-Pyrénées geographical article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
